MyBroadband’s speed test platform gives you the ability to test your Internet connection speed, and rate your Internet service provider (ISP). These consumer ratings are used to compile monthly and quarterly reports which rank South African Internet service providers. To ensure a neutral testing environment, MyBroadband’s speed test servers are hosted in Teraco’s vendor-neutral data centres. Through NAPAfrica, all network operators present at its peering points are provided with a free 10Gbps connection to MyBroadband’s speed test platform. MyBroadband is giving away prizes worth R5,000, including cash and gadgets, to encourage users to do a speed test. To stand a chance to win one of these great prizes, here is what you should do: The giveaway will run until 17 June 2019, and the winners will be announced shortly afterwards.